Params: {3: "As you advance with Jetavie into the factory's deepest section, a bizarre stage bathed in flashing lights assaults your vision."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Jetavie', 3: "...This old man just keeps laughing. There's no way to communicate with him.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Jetavie readies her Greatsword with a swing, looking eager to engage.'}
{2: 'Jetavie', 3: "I've merged with the Matrix's computing power, plus I have the Chosen One by my side. The Jetavie you see now is basically a mini mobile Matrix, you know?", 4: '1'}
